description: Amundi MSCI Europe Ex Switzerland ESG Selection - UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the MSCI Europe ex Switzerland ESG Selection P-Series 5% Issuer Capped Index (the Index), and to minimize the tracking error between the net asset value of the Sub-Fund and the performance of the Index. The anticipated level of tracking error, under normal market conditions, is indicated in the prospectus of the Sub-Fund. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi MSCI Europe Ex Switzerland ESG Selection UCITS ETF DR (C)
